{"tid":660117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太陽能「劉江華」自動開蓋壓縮垃圾 每個盛惠2.9萬","createTime":"2018-05-10T12:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T12:20:11.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb886c6f2b1574e33ab034ce94f7102f8a792dfb","tid":660117,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180510/large/1525944631_170b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180510%2Flarge%2F1525944631_170b.jpg&h=f6a7a2c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府推動香港變成智慧城市，食環署今年二月起，逐步在12個偏遠垃圾站引入24部太陽能壓縮垃圾桶，利用再生能源將家居垃圾壓縮處理，整個計劃斥資69萬元，即平均每個太陽能垃圾桶造價近2.9萬元，較傳統垃圾桶每個約700元貴逾40倍。有傳媒測試發現，新款垃圾桶未能壓縮垃圾，亦很少市民使用，運作成效存疑。<br />\n<br />\n這批新款垃圾桶位於西貢南圍、大坑徑、大埔頭村北、烏溪沙村和上環列提頓道的垃圾站，外型是藍色，垃圾桶設自動感應裝置，無須用手推開蓋。桶頂有太陽能發電，產生的電力將垃圾壓縮處理。而新垃圾桶的投放口只有35厘米高和45厘米闊，雖然較一般街邊垃圾桶37厘米乘19厘米大，但與660公升大型流動垃圾桶相比，投放口就較小。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒測試發現，新款垃圾桶很少人使用，即使已滿載，未見自動壓縮垃圾功能，有市民質疑設置高科技垃圾桶是浪費公帑。食環署回應稱，已向村代表和街坊代表提供宣傳教育，太陽能壓縮垃圾桶尚在試驗階段，署方會適時檢視成效，並考慮是否需要擴展計劃。<br />\n<br />\n除了太陽能壓縮垃圾桶外，食環署亦試行使用小型掃街車，又研究可否引入吸垃圾機、小型垃圾壓縮斗等其他機械或設備。署方早前回覆立法會指，正物色合適的設備或機器街道潔淨，例如將吹葉機、手推式小型掃地機及高速自轉式高壓清洗盤，加入新的街道潔淨服務合約中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180510/58174792?_ga=2.116841935.857830301.1525858086-396039381.1507615183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58174792%3F_ga%3D2.116841935.857830301.1525858086-396039381.1507615183&d=m%2F6%2BbClpgv5GVoVxpEBIjRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=d777dd3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58174792%3F_ga%3D2.116841935.857830301.1525858086-396039381.1507615183&h=a082e4b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180510/58174792?_ga=2.116841935.857830301.1525858086-396039381.1507615183</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180510/large/1525937150_482f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180510%2Flarge%2F1525937150_482f.png&h=16d52ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個窿咁細點用"},{"pid":"9fb09afe077792d74e2382e37827c0102ba51ae2","tid":660117,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"屙屎屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81731438f6e36098243628f3b2bb0d7b98fe2e86","tid":660117,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"已經平過d欄杆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23b91797d51287f1e300c7bfa3b7ed9413f44fc","tid":660117,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"太陽能板好快變成煙灰盅"},{"pid":"a2b6adf23701d7c89d803f451bf6be457e22f07a","tid":660117,"uid":13205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/disney/images/2/2b/Wall-E.png/revision/latest?cb=20151002192237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fdisney%2Fimages%2F2%2F2b%2FWall-E.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20151002192237&h=a4c2c233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9c2c72fcc98f0c05e88818c6205cd60e127b8bd","tid":660117,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"同之前嗰啲起完又拆<br />\n又坐唔到人嘅椅一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee407d055e4bf32047e2a869a0d2831f3a41b04","tid":660117,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23b91797d51287f1e300c7bfa3b7ed9413f44fc","tid":660117,"uid":80072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":